ActIndian Act
SubjectTobique First Nation ** Settlement Agreement **
PrecisOrder (a) authorizing the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to enter into, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, the Tobique First Nation 1892 Surrender Settlement Agreement between Canada and the Tobique First Nation; and (b) accepting the absolute surrender, pursuant to sections 38 and 39 of the Indian Act, of the lands described in Schedule B to the Order in Council.
